data.text: @clebeuva I got done in January because I work in social care. I had the Pfizer and other than a sore arm, I was completely fine. Nads had the Astra Zeneca yesterday and he's been fine too but I'm told its the 2nd dose which kicks your butt, so I will let you know 😆

@mel_shad Good stuff. Were you affected by the first one?

Think I've got about 2-3 weeks before I can book my first.
